  "short_text": "Extract Vowels from Word",
  "content": "Write a program that reads an string and finds all vowels in it. The program should output the vowels found in the input string.\n\n---\n\n#### Input\n\nThe input contains a single string.\n\n---\n\n#### Output\n\nThe vowels from the string, each separated by a space, on one line.\n\n---\n\n#### Explanation\n\nIf the input is:\n\n```\nPython\n```\n\nThe output should be:\n\n```\no\n```\n\n\n\n\n\n\n",
  "question_type": "CODING",
  "content_type": "MARKDOWN",
